---
title: BeaconLink Agent State Machine
---

stateDiagram-v2
    direction LR

    %% =====================================================
    %% Initial Bootstrap
    %% =====================================================

    [*] --> Starting

    Starting : Initialize Process
    Starting : Load Configuration
    Starting : Initialize Logging
    Starting : Initialize Local Storage

    Starting --> LoadingConfiguration

    LoadingConfiguration : Read Bootstrap Config
    LoadingConfiguration : Load Certificates
    LoadingConfiguration : Load Runtime Settings

    LoadingConfiguration --> Initializing

    Initializing : Initialize Components
    Initializing : Runtime Manager
    Initializing : Plugin Framework
    Initializing : Relay Client

    %% =====================================================
    %% Registration Phase
    %% =====================================================

    Initializing --> ConnectingRelay

    ConnectingRelay : Establish mTLS Connection
    ConnectingRelay : Authenticate Relay

    ConnectingRelay --> Registering : Connection Established
    ConnectingRelay --> RetryBackoff : Connection Failed

    Registering : Register with Control Plane
    Registering : Advertise Capabilities
    Registering : Publish Runtime Metadata

    Registering --> Synchronizing : Registration Approved
    Registering --> RegistrationRejected : Registration Failed

    RegistrationRejected : Policy Denied
    RegistrationRejected : Authentication Failed

    RegistrationRejected --> RetryBackoff

    %% =====================================================
    %% Initial Synchronization
    %% =====================================================

    Synchronizing : Download Desired State
    Synchronizing : Download Policies
    Synchronizing : Download Configuration

    Synchronizing --> Ready

    %% =====================================================
    %% Operational States
    %% =====================================================

    state Ready {

        [*] --> Idle

        Idle : Waiting for Events
        Idle : Heartbeats
        Idle : Observe Desired State

        Idle --> Reconciling : Desired State Changed
        Idle --> ExecutingWorkflow : Workflow Assigned
        Idle --> SecretResolution : Secret Required
        Idle --> Updating : Agent Upgrade
        Idle --> Degraded : Runtime Warning

        Reconciling : Continuous Reconciliation
        Reconciling : Drift Detection
        Reconciling : State Comparison

        Reconciling --> Deploying : Changes Required
        Reconciling --> Idle : State Converged

        Deploying : Execute Deployment
        Deploying : Apply Immutable Revision

        Deploying --> Verifying

        Verifying : Health Validation
        Verifying : Runtime Verification

        Verifying --> Idle : Successful
        Verifying --> Rollback : Verification Failed

        Rollback : Restore Previous Revision

        Rollback --> Idle
        Rollback --> Failed : Rollback Failed

        ExecutingWorkflow : Execute Workflow Task
        ExecutingWorkflow --> Idle : Completed
        ExecutingWorkflow --> Failed : Workflow Failed

        SecretResolution : Resolve Secrets
        SecretResolution --> Idle : Secrets Available
        SecretResolution --> Failed : Resolution Failed

        Updating : Self Update
        Updating --> Restarting

        Degraded : Partial Functionality
        Degraded --> Idle : Recovered
        Degraded --> Failed : Critical Failure

    }

    %% =====================================================
    %% Maintenance States
    %% =====================================================

    Restarting : Restart Agent
    Restarting --> Starting

    RetryBackoff : Exponential Backoff
    RetryBackoff --> ConnectingRelay

    %% =====================================================
    %% Failure States
    %% =====================================================

    Failed : Agent Unable to Continue
    Failed : Await Recovery
    Failed : Emit Failure Events

    Failed --> Restarting : Automatic Recovery
    Failed --> ShuttingDown : Stop Requested

    %% =====================================================
    %% Shutdown
    %% =====================================================

    ShuttingDown : Stop Heartbeats
    ShuttingDown : Finish Active Tasks
    ShuttingDown : Cleanup Secrets
    ShuttingDown : Close Runtime Connections

    ShuttingDown --> Terminated

    Terminated : Process Exited

    Terminated --> [*]

    %% =====================================================
    %% Global Transitions
    %% =====================================================

    Ready --> ShuttingDown : Graceful Shutdown
    ConnectingRelay --> ShuttingDown : Stop Requested
    RetryBackoff --> ShuttingDown : Stop Requested
    Synchronizing --> ShuttingDown : Stop Requested
    Initializing --> ShuttingDown : Stop Requested
    Starting --> ShuttingDown : Stop Requested